
1. customerList (lwc)
  - exposed on the Reservation Manager Lightning App Page
  - contains the customerTile value template
  - publishes an event when a record is clicked
  - refreshes when receiving the Flow_Status_Change__c event
    - this ensures the list only has Customers that are ready for a Reservation
  - currently supports Lead/Contact
  - Related Files:
    1. ReservationManagerController
      - returns a list of Customers (Contacts/Leads) that are in 'DraftStatus'
      - this controller also has responsibilities for reservationList, which isn't great.
